{
  "stem": "24106.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was, like, in a place that they go entertain the troops, like you have here Bob Hope.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That help-- that saved him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was constantly working, you know, travelling around, and entertaining the troops.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that saved him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he wants to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he came back, and he came out to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was a very handsome man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And a month later we were married.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband had a few cousins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All-- everybody survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They all-- all from Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't have no family, just except my-- my-- my mother, my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A distant cousin came also, you know, my father's-- from my father's side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a nice wedding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother was preparing the whole wedding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have a regular wedding with a rabbi, [INAUDIBLE] Rovno, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He gave us [NON-ENGLISH] Kiddushin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still have the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I have.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the chuppah was outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We remain about another month.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were, all in all, we were about seven months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we-- we said, we decided we want to go to the free world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We don't want to stay in Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We want to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So in order to go, you have to go first to Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came with my mother, my father, my sister, and my husband.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to a town, Bytom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we went to Zabrze.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Zabrze, was kibbutz already, you know, for all  the survivors from all our people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They form a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took us into the-- to that kibbutz, and I start traveling with them, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you didn't stay in one place too long, because everything was illegal going to Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just illegal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in order to, you have to still work in the-- be in the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
